warn.title: Partial translation warning
warn.desc: We want to inform you that some sections of the website are not fully translated because certain data obtained from our API is in English. We recommend that you use your browser's translator for a better experience. Thank you for your understanding and patience, and we apologize for the circumstance.

tooMany.title: Too many requests
tooMany.desc: It seems to me that you went too far with the requests. Better watch the streams of your favorite VTubers and come back in a few minutes. Don't cry either.

docs.title: Documentation
docs.desc: Explore our documentation to learn about every aspect of our API! From describing endpoints to examples of requests and responses, our documentation will guide you in the correct use of the API. Whether you are a beginner or an experienced developer, here you will find all the information you need to integrate our API into your projects efficiently and effectively.
